---
import Base from "../layouts/base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="What You'll Get with Discovery-as-a-Service"
  description="See what support looks like from Day 1 to Day 90 with Clarity.'s on-demand Discovery-as-a-Service."
  type="WebPage"
  canonicalURL="https://getclarity.win/what-you-get"
>
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-20 text-center">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
      What You'll Get with Discovery-as-a-Service
    </h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
      Strategic insight, delivered as a service. Support that fits your world,
      not the other way round.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 1: How it starts -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 mb-20 text-left">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-start">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">What happens after you join</h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-4">
          Within a day or two, we'll connect with you and get just enough
          context to start making a difference. No forms. No lengthy onboarding.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg">
          You'll feel the shift early. One message, one moment of clarity, one
          helpful decision at a time.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-[#A7D5F2] dark:bg-[#5AA6D6]">
        <p class="font-semibold mb-2 text-center">
          In your first 90 days, you'll:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-outside pl-5 text-left text-base space-y-2">
          <li>Unblock what matters most. Fast.</li>
          <li>Prioritise with confidence, not noise.</li>
          <li>Spot risks before they turn into rework.</li>
          <li>Make clear, accountable decisions that scale.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 2: What we give you -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 mb-20 text-left">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-start">
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-[#75C1E8] dark:bg-[#429EDB] text-white">
        <p class="font-semibold mb-2 text-center">You'll get access to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-outside pl-5 text-left text-base space-y-2">
          <li>A dedicated expert who understands your goals.</li>
          <li>Timely, decision-ready input. No chasing, no waffle.</li>
          <li>Insight you can forward, not just understand.</li>
          <li>Pragmatic tools that help (only when they help).</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">
          This isn't about presentations
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-4">
          Briefs, radars, and sessions help, but they're not the product.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg">
          What matters is what they unlock: clearer judgment, stronger
          decisions, and momentum that lasts.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-20">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">
      Your First 90 Days with Clarity.
    </h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-left">
      <!-- 30 Day Block -->
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-[#A7D5F2] dark:bg-[#5AA6D6]">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">First 30 Days</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-outside pl-5 space-y-2 text-base">
          <li>Understand what's urgent, what's noisy, and what's missing.</li>
          <li>Clear the noise.</li>
          <li>Make one good decision with confidence.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- 60 Day Block -->
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-[#75C1E8] dark:bg-[#429EDB] text-white">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Next 30 Days</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-outside pl-5 space-y-2 text-base">
          <li>Get strategic breathing room.</li>
          <li>Re-align teams and priorities.</li>
          <li>Spot risks and patterns early.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- 90 Day Block -->
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-[#429EDB]/10 dark:bg-[#1F78C1]/20">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Final 30 Days</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-outside pl-5 space-y-2 text-base">
          <li>Build momentum behind decisions.</li>
          <li>Scale up what's working.</li>
          <li>Lock in your new way of thinking.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="text-center text-lg mt-10 max-w-xl mx-auto">
      You don't need to follow this to the day. But most clients feel this
      rhythm. Quick relief, clearer focus, lasting confidence.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 3: Final reassurance -->
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-10 text-center">
    <p class="text-xl font-medium mb-6">
      You don't need to figure everything out. You just need to get started.
    </p>
    <p class="text-lg mb-8">
      With Clarity., you don't just get answers. You get a thinking partner who
      earns your trust, fits your rhythm, and adds momentum. No blockers. No
      drama. Just support that sticks.
    </p>
    <!-- <a
      href="/support-plans-preview-93xz4/"
      class="inline-block px-6 py-3 rounded-xl bg-[#429EDB] text-white font-semibold hover:bg-[#1F78C1] transition"
    >
      View Support Plans
    </a> -->
  </section>

  <!-- Navigation Arrows -->
  <section class="my-8 flex flex-col items-center gap-4 text-center">
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
      Want to know more about Discovery-as-a-Service?
    </p>
    <div class="flex gap-12 justify-center items-center">
      <!-- Left Arrow Link -->
      <a
        href="/why-clarity-works/"
        aria-label="Previous page"
        class="hover:text-blue-600 transition"
      >
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          width="64"
          height="64"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path>
        </svg>
      </a>

      <!-- Right Arrow Link -->
      <a
        href="/daas/"
        aria-label="Next page"
        class="hover:text-blue-600 transition"
      >
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          width="64"
          height="64"
        >
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"
          ></path>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="text-center mb-24">
    <h2 class="text-xl mb-4 font-semibold">Ready?</h2>
    <a
      href="/"
      class="inline-block bg-[#429EDB] text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded hover:bg-[#1F78C1] transition"
    >
      Join the Waitlist
    </a>
  </div>
</Base>
